=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋有冇話邊款頭易gel d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4a698aca8ee4103882bc5d9468a3683bc87ec4","tid":142472,"uid":31105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:17:57.000Z","msg":"Hairjam 藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2b10303015c111ba7c0edd05a5968fbee3b35e","tid":142472,"uid":68592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hairjam 藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGatsby? 藍色係咪真係個頭會變藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fbef13d51dd78156ade471387c82143580a541","tid":142472,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Hairjam 藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGatsby? 藍色係咪真係個頭會變藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 係個力度嘅分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhairjam gel出嚟比較自然 不過全部都冇乜力<br />\ngel日本仔束感頭嘅話 唔太適合"},{"pid":"49de1a11e9a70e51e22bbec8ac38364646ffc2d5","tid":142472,"uid":68592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Hairjam 藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGatsby? 藍色係咪真係個頭會變藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 係個力度嘅分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhairjam gel出嚟比較自然 不過全部都冇乜力<br />\ngel日本仔束感頭嘅話 唔太適合</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打gel開咩頭？油頭？"},{"pid":"eaf3d4f61e24b012e34e2aea5eadac96293d26a7","tid":142472,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下gatsby係咪唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngatsby算ok可以接受 唔算差 但唔太好 有部分產品好傷髮</blockquote><br />\n顏色蠟新手玩一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泥就&hellip;好撚難洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實巴打gel咩款嘅頭？唔同頭用唔同野 好難就咁答</blockquote><br />\n我係新手gel頭，所以唔知可以點gel,上網睇教學d人好似好易gel,但我學佢地咁又覺得gel得奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋有冇話邊款頭易gel d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇話嘅 咩頭都有自己嘅技巧<br />\nspiky 層次 露額 樣樣都有唔同technique<br />\n有冇圖/畫 比我地睇下你而家個頭係點？<br />\n咁會易答d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4219416331245ba2a41fd52de2c9f0231dd528cd","tid":142472,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Hairjam 藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGatsby? 藍色係咪真係個頭會變藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係 係個力度嘅分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhairjam gel出嚟比較自然 不過全部都冇乜力<br />\ngel日本仔束感頭嘅話 唔太適合</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打gel開咩頭？油頭？</blockquote><br />\n上面個巴打應該係<br />\n我gel日本仔頭(好似係)"},{"pid":"e83b420565c1784d2910df0c751ff5df72d9f5b1","tid":142472,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"btw hairjam真係試得過<br />\n因為佢整出嚟自然同唔黏 所以整柒咗都有個譜 唔會一pat野咁<br />\n不過睇埋你頭髮長度 先睇買咩顏色"},{"pid":"c66dc03073f0cd9185c025ff77e2d815a3fe6512","tid":142472,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw hairjam真係試得過<br />\n因為佢整出嚟自然同唔黏 所以整柒咗都有個譜 唔會一pat野咁<br />\n不過睇埋你頭髮長度 先睇買咩顏色</blockquote><br />\n不過Gatsby始終俾人個感覺太新手feel <br />\n雖然都係gel到(gel頭好講手勢)，但都係硬係差咁啲嘢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddd6e8f5131eaf29cab8bd2ec37159f24ab1ecd","tid":142472,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋用髮泥定髮蠟定其他造型產品</blockquote><br />\n我用開wax，同埋研究緊啲力度有咩唔同"},{"pid":"5977867d92bbcdbf677a482b944d61a4c7f2a70e","tid":142472,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下gatsby係咪唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngatsby算ok可以接受 唔算差 但唔太好 有部分產品好傷髮</blockquote><br />\n顏色蠟新手玩一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泥就&hellip;好撚難洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實巴打gel咩款嘅頭？唔同頭用唔同野 好難就咁答</blockquote><br />\n我係新手gel頭，所以唔知可以點gel,上網睇教學d人好似好易gel,但我學佢地咁又覺得gel得奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最主要係要練習多啲<span style=\"color: red;\">gel頭手勢</span>，同埋睇下你個風筒夠唔夠力吹得起你個頭，然後就睇下產品係咪合適；其次洗頭方面要做足功夫，睇下有冇用護髮素令髮質變得容易造型。其實仲有好多好多因素影響個造型容唔容易gel，做足以上嘅話，基本上都唔會浪費好時間去gel，亦同時得心應手。"}]}